name: Mitsubishi Electric Q61P-A2 (Refurbished)- Power Supply Module
description: The Mitsubishi Q61P-A2 is a power supply module for the System Q series PLC family. There are a number of power supply modules for users to choose from which ensures their PLC is receiving the amount of power they need for their modules. The PSU module supplies power to the modules slotted into the base unit. At least one power supply module is needed for the base rack and for some extension base units. Each of these power supply modules have a red LED to indicate readiness for operation.
